data.description: LUXURY, LAND AND LONGHORNS! Welcome to your exquisite and rare 15-acre Texas estate conveniently positioned between our quaint German town of New Braunfels and the gateway to the Hill Country town of Spring Branch! Your luxury lifestyle includes a beautiful Tuscan-inspired farm house with a flexible floorplan and room for all. You will appreciate creating memories with friends, family and colleagues in your own private Hill Country oasis. Superb Texas size living, land, storage and entertaining spaces. Your spectacular outdoor entertaining area is fun and stylish and is accentuated with three fire features and large covered kitchen area with all the essentials. Al fresco dining is enjoyable as your entire patio and pool area is surrounded by a flying insect repellent system with automatic timer. Your inviting, 35,000 gallon, heated, lagoon-style pool features a beach entry, bubblers, submerged bar seating, eight-foot diving end, fitness swim jets, infinity edge and adjoining extra deep spa with cascading water. A beautiful curved staircase with wrought iron joins the upper and lower patio areas. At night, you may choose to just relax as you gaze at the stars and planets from your second story terrace. Your property is fenced and cross-fenced and ready for your horses, cows, goats, donkeys and chickens. Or, just simply enjoy the herd of majestic longhorns that roam the neighborhood. Your private well accesses the Edwards Aquifer directly and will easily meet your water needs. Your 1250 square-foot barn, set away from the home, showcases dual rolling overhead doors, epoxy flooring and halogen lights and easily accommodates your toys and equipment.  WELCOME TO TEXAS.
